-mtime -1     -mtime 1         -mtime +1( 1 day ago)
-mtime 0 üëâ today since midnight
| Syntax      | Meaning                                 |
| ----------- | --------------------------------------- |
| `-mtime -N` | Modified **less than N+1 days ago**     |
| `-mtime N`  | Modified **between N and N+1 days ago** |
| `-mtime +N` | Modified **more than N+1 days ago**     |


